  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In previous studies, 90% of patients who underwent elective cardiopulmonary bypass procedure
      manifested CD4 counts of less than 500 cells/microliter in the immediate (day 1)
      post-operative period. This study will investigate whether or not Nelfinavir increases those
      CD4 counts in the post-operative period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
